{"tid":947513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Space X投資者懷疑馬斯克 挪用資金於隧道項目","createTime":"2018-12-19T10:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T11:17:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"14057fe0975b99c3338bc211d28473d942a20a7a","tid":947513,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2018/12/19/phpj7SFFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F19%2Fphpj7SFFM.jpg&h=ed894093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬斯克日前宣佈，旗下無聊公司的洛杉磯隧道已完工。（路透）<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕日前特斯拉執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）表示，旗下無聊公司（Boring Company）的洛杉磯隧道項目已完工，並宣佈於本月開放展示。不過現無聊公司卻被外媒爆出，該公司挪用馬斯克另一家旗下公司Space X的部分資金與開發人力，來建造這條地下隧道。消息一出，馬斯克陷入投資者信任危機。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，有Space X投資者發現，他們在Space X投資的部分資源流進無聊公司，並被拿來開發隧道，像是Space X開發人員，以及使用Space X資金購買的巨型隧道挖掘機設備。對於無聊公司花著Space X投資者投入的資源，來開發自己公司的項目，獲利卻未回饋這些Space X投資人，引發投資者爭議。<br />\n<br />\n其中最令人爭議的是，馬斯克擁有超過9成的無聊公司股權，因此只要有獲利，馬斯克將成為最大受益者，這也讓投資者更質疑無聊公司挪用Space X資源的行為。對此Space X拒絕回應，而馬斯克則對此澄清，表示這是誤導性的新聞。<br />\n<br />\n但其實這並不是馬斯克第1次在其旗下不同公司之間挪動資金，有外媒報導，馬斯克在特斯拉發展初期，就曾用自己名義向Space X借了2000萬美元來資助特斯拉。對此Space X最大投資者Peter Thiel創始人基金，曾就Space X資源轉移的問題表示擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2646598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2646598&d=eMUFNY%2B73ln4lj6gV8ZHxZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8f37ac5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2646598&h=5d8b943b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2646598</a>"},{"pid":"07a27613cdc168d65b64528ac657d013bd5a1a8c","tid":947513,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"無聊公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e34a7258c38c1eea06308cf26e52ad559e410f0","tid":947513,"uid":177724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"In a statement to The Journal, Peter Thiel&rsquo;s firm, Founders Fund, said it had &ldquo;no concerns.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"19730d3c9ef5c7d2b003179fb871b1b69f22ac98","tid":947513,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a27613cdc168d65b64528ac657d013bd5a1a8c","tid":947513,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"無聊公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dfdbb36da0ee4f5a569b69042f9df98f843b62","tid":947513,"uid":39387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a27613cdc168d65b64528ac657d013bd5a1a8c","tid":947513,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"無聊公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"點解會咁翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8ec8628f6cf936aa07269a43b4d96a9761719b","tid":947513,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"天才唔應該受呢啲庸俗制度所限<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56498e6b4685042787ec29c735bbef8069356a4","tid":947513,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10f4b20356ff1cf32ed9b43a246d889c49552e72","tid":947513,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/boringcompany/status/1075318894871470081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fboringcompany%2Fstatus%2F10753188948714